{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5d2e77843","title":"江西省波阳县皇岗区东溪乡“文革”中非正常死亡人档案 -- 徐宗镜","origin":"根据档案材料翻印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"547cfcab84","index":0,"year":1986,"month":3,"day":25,"articleId":"f5d2e77843"}],"tags":[{"id":"9073865ccd","name":"江西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5f6dd44d4d","type":"title","text":"江西省波阳县皇岗区东溪乡“文革”中非正常死亡人档案 -- 徐宗镜","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"2cc061bd6c","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名：徐宗镜","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"834ed04161","type":"paragraph","text":"性别：男","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1c926d1499","type":"paragraph","text":"籍贯：江西波阳","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"43171bc6bb","type":"appellation","text":"住址：东溪石板桥村","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"a3e5cb40f5","type":"paragraph","text":"1986年3月25日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"f2335e4c55","type":"subtitle","text":"关于徐宗镜在“文革”中非正常死亡情况调查","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"70ed3b1448","type":"subtitle","text":"东溪乡核查小组","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"98014bbf24","type":"subtitle","text":"1986年3月25日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"38d40bf8ac","type":"subtitle","text":"关于徐宗镜在“文革”中死亡情况的调查报告","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"f810fab05b","type":"paragraph","text":"死者徐宗镜，男性，享年56岁，家庭出身地主，家住东溪乡东溪村委会石板桥村，1970年3月死亡。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1f98df5d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"1970年3月间，东溪大队假石板桥村村背后晒场上召开斗争大会，徐宗镜因现反问题，由下炉村程景文、高发盛（民兵排长）二人从下炉村带到石板桥参加斗争会接受斗争，会上石板桥村徐宗林老婆张爱荣诉说徐宗镜解放前霸占了其夫前妻，诉苦后用拳头打了徐宗镜的头上，当时流了血，据张爱荣本人讲是手指上戴了戒指，所以打破皮流血，不一会徐宗镜昏倒，在场大会主持人，当时东溪大队党支部书记刘正明（已死亡）说他装死不老实，把他从台上拎起，朝其小腹部踢了一脚，人就不行了，会就散了。以后徐宗镜慢慢走回家（下炉村）走到上炉村不能走，其子用土车推其回家，回家后说腹中痛不能上床睡，用几把稻草睡在锅头边，第三天即死亡。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"655412526a","type":"paragraph","text":"根据上述情况，我们认为徐宗镜属于非正常死亡，其死因主要是头部和腹部受伤致死，但因刘正明已死，无追究责任必要。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"3592c88990","type":"paragraph","text":"特此报告。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"bb0ed6f3e1","type":"paragraph","text":" 调查人：徐显华、程元默1986年3月25日","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"5362022b47","type":"paragraph","text":"经党委审查同意调查人意见。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"2b29742370","type":"paragraph","text":" 86.4.16","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"270b684107","type":"subtitle","text":"谈话笔录","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"332c94d385","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1986.3.21","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"e4d45a9e76","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：下炉村程景旺家","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"3253c6e4fe","type":"paragraph","text":"询问人：徐显华","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"419f90828b","type":"paragraph","text":"被询问人：程景贵，现年41岁，家住下炉村，中共党员。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1c0a84e642","type":"paragraph","text":"记录：程元默","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"a553d0b405","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你认识徐宗镜吗？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"0f69209dc0","type":"paragraph","text":"答：认识。因我当时是生产队长，他是我队社员。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"9ecba70b66","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你知道徐宗镜被批斗的最后一次情况吗？","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"84c4968e0c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：知道一些。记得那天大概是1970－1971年3－4月左右，头天在上坂时他对我说：今年我可能要死，我说不会，一点风寒病很快就会好的。第二天在早上8点钟左右，由高发盛和程景文二人把他带到大队部，石板桥村批斗。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"ea3f57ad6a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你参加了当时的斗争会吗？","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"18c5bd1e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：参加了。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"81e79aea06","type":"paragraph","text":"问：大会主持人是谁？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"5f4d5f41e2","type":"paragraph","text":"答：刘正明、刘文华。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"ccd3d48192","type":"paragraph","text":"问：在斗争会上你看到有什么人打了徐宗镜？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"aa9af80bd3","type":"paragraph","text":"答：石板桥徐宗林老婆张爱荣打了徐宗镜的头一下，当时就流血，因我在台下没有看清用什么打的。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"844bf474fc","type":"paragraph","text":"问：其他还有什么人打了吗？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1c192f85a4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：一些人还拳打脚踢，具体是什么人记不清楚。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"a85a698816","type":"paragraph","text":"问：徐宗镜被斗回家后的情况你知道吗？","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"90fc0a6cc9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他回家后没有上床睡，他儿子用几把稻草把他睡在锅头边。第二天我到他家去看，稻草都因为痛苦而搞得乱七八糟，当时我问他是什么地方痛，他说是肚子痛，不能上床睡。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"0e25b2534c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：第三天死的情况你知道吗？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"70e4e63ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他是第三天清早死的，死后他儿子向队讨了几块板，随便钉了一个匣子，草草掩埋。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"f64308a9f3","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你还听说什么吗？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"3487c1c999","type":"paragraph","text":"答：其他没有什么。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"89e518f039","type":"paragraph","text":" 被询问人：程景贵","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"6314aa5944","type":"subtitle","text":"谈话笔录","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"e4f2531d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1986.3.20","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"84f2e22a55","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：本人家中","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"7053b7d894","type":"paragraph","text":"询问人：徐显华","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"b36b53cd21","type":"paragraph","text":"被询问人：徐彦富，现年66岁，家住东溪村委会刘家旺村，贫农。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"a61a4fc92a","type":"paragraph","text":"记录：程元默","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1a20200006","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你认识徐宗镜吗？","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1d2405b9b5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：认识，我和他是老邻居，在三查当中是经常在一起挨斗的。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"54e3935914","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你知道徐宗镜是怎样死的？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"bb5fd8e05d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：知道。我是在皇岗回家走在上炉村关山口遇见徐宗镜的，他是被批斗回家（因那次我没有参加批斗），他对我说：老弟，我喊叫你坐一下，我现在与你见面，以后怕是不能见面了，我问他什么原因，他说今天的斗争大会被人打伤，并叫我帮他包一下伤口，我一看他的头一个洞正往外流花脓，可能是脑浆，我给他包了一下，然后我就回了家，三天后他儿子到石板桥搞松树回去割棺才，告诉我说他父亲死了。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"c155cb7070","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他告诉你是谁打了他吗？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"4465f5b898","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他只是这样说：是刘正明叫他们打我的，他并踢了我一脚，打破头的人他没有告诉我，只是说不知被什么人打了一下，就昏了过去。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"40a094613c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：当时是什么时间？","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"ebdc35c74c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：三查运动开始的第二年，3－4月左右。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"86b8595d66","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你还知道什么吗？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"6ac8a8f69b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：因我没参加会，其它就不知道。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"7fecf61dcf","type":"paragraph","text":" 被询问人：徐彦富","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"7d2fe18422","type":"subtitle","text":"谈话笔录","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"504cf4215f","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1986.3.20","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"9d97b323c1","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：东溪村委会","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"f158931673","type":"paragraph","text":"询问人：徐显华","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"d202a3db34","type":"paragraph","text":"被询问人：徐良根","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"52393eb677","type":"paragraph","text":"记录：程元默","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"2bc29e531a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你知道徐宗镜的死因吗？","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"baeb998996","type":"paragraph","text":"答：知道。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"df6821d6ff","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你与死者是什么关系？当时多大年纪？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"d873b7515a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我与死者是父子关系，当时22岁。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"1745cfceb0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你谈谈死因的详细情况。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"2abd6c1c6a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我父亲是1971年4月在家死亡，我记得我父亲是在参加东溪大队斗争会后，回家三天后死亡，当时的斗争会放在东溪大队石板桥村召开，我父亲是被斗争者，其罪名是被说成是在1968年参加了反革命组织，从那以后就经常被批斗。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"2a1bebba4a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：在最后的一次斗争会上，你记不记得你父亲当时被斗争的情况？","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"03d99595b9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：因当时我不能参加大会，事后听他人说：我父亲在被斗争时，被张爱荣（石板桥村，徐宗林老婆）用秤砣打破了头。还有不少人用拳打脚踢，回家后三天就死亡。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"56b0741f8b","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你父亲被斗回家后与你说过什么，或请医师看过吗？","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"af3d6a7982","type":"paragraph","text":"答：父亲没说什么。在当时情况下请不到医师。伤又十分严重，头顶被打开一个洞，肚子被人踢后呈现肿胀，我当时很着急，只好眼看着父亲慢慢离去。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"f52c24e984","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你还知道什么吗？还有什么要说吗？","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"78c35ee47e","type":"paragraph","text":"答：不知道。我只是要求政府调查处理。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"},{"id":"3df75301ea","type":"paragraph","text":" 被询问人签名：徐良根","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843"}],"page":{"id":"19e6723401","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f5d2e77843","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}